Text:
buyer: got any magic mushrooms?

peddler: no, but I got some dwarf moss, oh, and they'll really blow you're head off though; look at this, the last time I took it I saw fairies for III days!

b: ha ha, nicey nice! roll us a giant!

p: got any money?
=======
nice to see two songs from POB; many thanks for sharing this compilation
